        "content": "**Q:** In what ratio must rice at ₹24/kg be mixed with rice at ₹30/kg to get a mixture worth ₹28/kg?\n**Solution:** (30 - 28):(28 - 24) = 2 : 4 = 1 : 2\n**Answer:** 1 : 2"
