    "subtopics": [
      {
        "subtopic": "Water Replacement",
        "content": "**Q:** A container contains 60 litres of milk. 10 litres are replaced with water. This is done 2 times. Find the quantity of milk left.\n**Solution:** 60 × (1 - 10/60)^2 = 60 × (5/6)^2 = 60 × 25/36 = 41.67 litres\n**Answer:** 41.67 litres"
      }
